00:29:24,325 --> 00:29:27,585
So I think there's real scope for other studios

605
00:29:27,625 --> 00:29:28,406
to do that kind of thing.

606
00:29:30,326 --> 00:29:33,407
And I think it really is skipping all the boring stuff.

